channel.title: Blue october
channel.description:
Anyone listen to these guys? There great to just mellow out to. I got the album Foiled. I downloaded it because it had platinum sales im gonna get another one. [img]http://a517.ac-images.myspacecdn.com/00827/61/57/827787516_m.jpg[/img]
Blue October is a rock band originally from Houston, Texas. The band is best known for the singles "Hate Me" and "Into the Ocean" from the album Foiled. The band was formed in 1995 and currently consists of Justin Furstenfeld (lead vocals), Jeremy Furstenfeld (drums, percussion), Ryan Delahoussaye (violin/viola, mandolin, keyboards, vocals), C.B. Hudson (guitar), and Matt Noveskey (bass guitar).
http://www.myspace.com/blueoctober
